WEBVTT

00:00:35.970 --> 00:00:38.770
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.770 --> 00:00:41.270
=Episode 12=

00:00:57.916 --> 00:00:59.583
Mr. Zhang is fishing. Don't approach.

00:01:13.416 --> 00:01:15.416
What brings you to me?

00:01:15.958 --> 00:01:16.416
My lord.

00:01:17.375 --> 00:01:19.500
I have always respected you

00:01:19.541 --> 00:01:20.291
as a kind elder.

00:01:21.291 --> 00:01:22.166
Keep it down.

00:01:23.041 --> 00:01:24.333
Don't scare my fish.

00:01:25.125 --> 00:01:26.125
You're

00:01:26.250 --> 00:01:28.916
always so restless. Get to the point.

00:01:30.125 --> 00:01:31.583
Even if you say the wrong thing,

00:01:31.875 --> 00:01:33.500
I won't blame you.

00:01:35.625 --> 00:01:36.541
My father's case.

00:01:37.166 --> 00:01:38.500
Does it have anything to do
with Lu Guokai?

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:42.708
It seems

00:01:43.958 --> 00:01:45.500
you still suspect Guokai.

00:01:46.333 --> 00:01:48.375
He altered Diaotu's case file.

00:01:49.083 --> 00:01:49.875
Did he...

00:01:50.500 --> 00:01:51.958
Did he alter my father's file too?

00:01:52.375 --> 00:01:53.750
Was he the one
who smeared my father's name?

00:01:53.875 --> 00:01:55.000
Was he the one who framed him?

00:01:55.750 --> 00:01:56.833
You have your reasons

00:01:57.458 --> 00:01:58.416
for suspecting him.

00:01:58.833 --> 00:02:00.583
But allow me to be fair.

00:02:01.083 --> 00:02:04.250
Lu Guokai may be harsh and petty,

00:02:04.791 --> 00:02:06.333
but he doesn't have a bad heart.

00:02:07.208 --> 00:02:08.041
For example,

00:02:09.166 --> 00:02:09.750
that day,

00:02:10.166 --> 00:02:11.583
he received word

00:02:11.916 --> 00:02:13.875
that you were in danger
at Marquis Taiping's manor.

00:02:14.250 --> 00:02:17.000
So he used Feng Fuliu as an excuse

00:02:17.208 --> 00:02:18.458
to go there and help you.

00:02:19.250 --> 00:02:19.916
Think about it.

00:02:20.250 --> 00:02:21.666
If Lu Guokai

00:02:22.041 --> 00:02:23.875
truly wished to harm others,

00:02:23.958 --> 00:02:26.875
he wouldn't have saved you
when he knew you were in danger.

00:02:28.333 --> 00:02:29.166
But Lu Guokai

00:02:29.166 --> 00:02:30.791
has altered case records before.

00:02:32.958 --> 00:02:34.208
If Lu Guokai

00:02:34.708 --> 00:02:36.666
is guilty of altering case files,

00:02:36.875 --> 00:02:38.166
then every one of us

00:02:38.708 --> 00:02:41.041
could be suspected of the same.

00:02:42.333 --> 00:02:43.083
Bingfan.

00:02:43.666 --> 00:02:44.541
Do you know

00:02:45.333 --> 00:02:47.750
that once you enter public service,
you are no longer your own master?

00:02:48.041 --> 00:02:49.041
Some things,

00:02:52.791 --> 00:02:54.083
for the sake of the greater good,

00:02:54.083 --> 00:02:55.833
can't be made public.

00:02:56.708 --> 00:02:57.291
Your father

00:02:57.958 --> 00:02:59.541
died in the line of duty.

00:02:59.833 --> 00:03:01.458
You should stop clinging to this.

00:03:02.958 --> 00:03:05.166
But my father wasn't treated fairly.

00:03:05.416 --> 00:03:06.125
His sacrifice

00:03:06.750 --> 00:03:08.208
only left him with a ruined name.

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:10.833
The mole still has not been found.

00:03:11.541 --> 00:03:13.208
Is this what you call the greater good?

00:03:20.291 --> 00:03:21.166
Bingfan.

00:03:23.166 --> 00:03:24.291
You are

00:03:25.375 --> 00:03:26.416
even more stubborn than your father.

00:03:29.470 --> 00:03:32.600
(Northern Bureau)

00:04:42.100 --> 00:04:43.666
(Spirit Tablet of My Sworn Brother,
Qianhu, Shen Lian)

00:04:43.666 --> 00:04:44.166
(Qianhu, Shen Lian)
(Father.)

00:05:03.833 --> 00:05:05.583
(Why would Lu Guokai keep)

00:05:05.750 --> 00:05:06.875
(my father's spirit tablet
in his secret room?)

00:05:33.850 --> 00:05:36.560
(Spirit Tablet of My Sworn Brother,
Qianhu, Shen Lian)

00:06:07.970 --> 00:06:09.291
(Treasure Pavilion)

00:06:09.291 --> 00:06:10.083
(Treasure Pavilion)
Returning the Azure Dragon Jade.

00:06:17.541 --> 00:06:18.791
The imperial Azure Dragon Jade.

00:06:19.416 --> 00:06:21.875
Feng Fuliu returned
the Azure Dragon Jade!

00:06:34.541 --> 00:06:35.541
I was going to scare you.

00:06:36.916 --> 00:06:37.333
What's wrong?

00:06:37.541 --> 00:06:38.541
Your face says you are unhappy.

00:06:39.791 --> 00:06:40.458
Chang Beiming.

00:06:41.041 --> 00:06:43.208
Usually, whose spirit tablet

00:06:43.541 --> 00:06:44.666
would you enshrine in your own room?

00:06:45.750 --> 00:06:46.500
A spirit tablet?

00:06:47.583 --> 00:06:48.541
A close family member.

00:06:49.166 --> 00:06:50.583
What if there is no blood relation?

00:06:51.583 --> 00:06:53.583
No blood relation?

00:06:54.166 --> 00:06:55.500
Then either a sworn friend

00:06:55.583 --> 00:06:56.958
or someone you wronged.

00:06:57.875 --> 00:07:00.583
Exactly. Guilt.

00:07:01.375 --> 00:07:02.833
That's why one would honor him
day and night

00:07:03.208 --> 00:07:04.416
to atone for one's guilt.

00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:07.833
Whose spirit tablet
are we talking about?

00:07:10.916 --> 00:07:11.666
I can't tell you.

00:07:12.166 --> 00:07:13.041
You can't?

00:07:13.541 --> 00:07:13.916
All right.

00:07:14.500 --> 00:07:16.708
Then where did you go last night,
leaving at the second watch

00:07:16.750 --> 00:07:17.333
and returning at the third?

00:07:18.416 --> 00:07:19.000
How do you know?

00:07:19.041 --> 00:07:20.208
I live next door.

00:07:27.541 --> 00:07:28.375
Bingfan.

00:07:29.250 --> 00:07:30.333
Your father's case

00:07:31.291 --> 00:07:33.375
is connected
to Prince Luo's treason case.

00:07:34.583 --> 00:07:36.041
I hope you take this step by step

00:07:36.416 --> 00:07:37.916
and don't rush.

00:07:38.416 --> 00:07:39.666
Otherwise, the truth you find

00:07:40.375 --> 00:07:41.500
may not be the one you want.

00:07:41.666 --> 00:07:44.041
Why is everyone trying to stop me
from finding the truth?

00:07:44.625 --> 00:07:46.541
We are not trying to stop you.

00:07:47.750 --> 00:07:50.125
But trying to stir up

00:07:50.833 --> 00:07:52.875
the Northern Bureau's muddy waters
all by yourself

00:07:53.208 --> 00:07:54.083
will be nearly impossible.

00:07:55.375 --> 00:07:56.458
Didn't Zhang Weimin say it?

00:07:57.833 --> 00:07:58.875
Start with Leng Xin.

00:08:01.083 --> 00:08:01.625
Leng Xin?

00:08:02.250 --> 00:08:02.708
Yes.

00:08:03.625 --> 00:08:04.333
Start with him

00:08:04.833 --> 00:08:05.833
and uncover the truth slowly.

00:08:06.333 --> 00:08:06.833
Otherwise,

00:08:07.708 --> 00:08:09.000
not only will you
never reach the truth,

00:08:11.416 --> 00:08:12.000
but you may

00:08:12.625 --> 00:08:13.541
also put your life in danger.

00:08:24.166 --> 00:08:24.875
You came to me?

00:08:28.833 --> 00:08:29.750
Who exactly are you?

00:08:31.458 --> 00:08:32.291
Do you really want to know?

00:09:02.166 --> 00:09:03.583
What's wrong, Bingfan?

00:09:05.208 --> 00:09:05.708
Nothing.

00:09:06.250 --> 00:09:06.666
Go to sleep.

00:09:17.250 --> 00:09:18.125
(Is it him?)

00:09:19.125 --> 00:09:19.958
(It shouldn't be.)

00:09:21.500 --> 00:09:23.541
(Then why does it feel like him
every time?)

00:09:25.430 --> 00:09:27.708
(Go with the Flow)

00:09:27.708 --> 00:09:28.250
(Go with the Flow)
Bingfan.

00:09:28.916 --> 00:09:29.958
This is Imperial Physician Xue.

00:09:30.458 --> 00:09:32.458
He is a master at treating palpitations
and insomnia.

00:09:33.291 --> 00:09:34.291
Thank you for your trouble,
Imperial Physician Xue.

00:09:35.416 --> 00:09:36.333
Miss, when

00:09:36.708 --> 00:09:37.916
did this illness begin?

00:09:38.500 --> 00:09:39.500
When I was fourteen.

00:09:39.708 --> 00:09:40.875
After a great tragedy struck my family.

00:09:41.500 --> 00:09:42.208
It has lasted until now.

00:09:44.416 --> 00:09:45.083
Miss,

00:09:45.750 --> 00:09:47.833
would you mind if I use hypnosis

00:09:47.833 --> 00:09:49.250
to explore the cause?

00:10:04.500 --> 00:10:05.083
Miss.

00:10:06.250 --> 00:10:07.833
In your mind,

00:10:08.458 --> 00:10:10.083
do you see

00:10:10.541 --> 00:10:12.291
a peaceful sea of flowers?

00:10:16.958 --> 00:10:19.708
There is a fourteen-year-old girl

00:10:20.166 --> 00:10:21.750
in that beautiful sea of flowers,

00:10:22.375 --> 00:10:23.791
chasing butterflies.

00:10:25.166 --> 00:10:27.541
That's you, Miss Shen.

00:10:32.583 --> 00:10:33.500
(Father!)

00:10:34.625 --> 00:10:35.541
(Mother!)

00:10:37.708 --> 00:10:38.750
(I'll kill you!)

00:10:39.083 --> 00:10:40.041
(I'll strangle you!)

00:10:40.666 --> 00:10:41.666
I'll kill you!

00:10:42.708 --> 00:10:43.708
I'll kill you!

00:10:44.791 --> 00:10:45.750
I'll kill you!

00:10:46.041 --> 00:10:46.958
I'll kill you!

00:10:47.208 --> 00:10:48.375
Help!

00:10:48.916 --> 00:10:49.666
I'll kill you!

00:10:50.416 --> 00:10:51.416
I'll kill you!

00:10:52.041 --> 00:10:52.666
I'll kill you!

00:10:58.625 --> 00:10:59.333
Imperial Physician Xue.

00:11:02.041 --> 00:11:03.208
Her inner demon is too strong.

00:11:03.500 --> 00:11:04.791
It has already wounded her mind.

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:06.083
Her insomnia

00:11:06.375 --> 00:11:08.458
can no longer be cured
by ordinary medicine.

00:11:09.875 --> 00:11:11.375
Imperial Physician Xue,
please forgive her.

00:11:12.583 --> 00:11:13.458
A wounded heart

00:11:14.041 --> 00:11:15.166
must heal from within.

00:11:15.291 --> 00:11:16.583
To heal her heart,

00:11:16.708 --> 00:11:17.791
you must first remove her
inner demon.

00:11:46.958 --> 00:11:47.541
Feng Fuliu!

00:11:49.083 --> 00:11:50.458
Not everyone with graceful footwork

00:11:50.458 --> 00:11:51.291
is Feng Fuliu.

00:12:00.958 --> 00:12:03.500
Please apologize to Physician Xue
for me.

00:12:05.791 --> 00:12:07.291
He has practiced medicine for decades.

00:12:07.500 --> 00:12:08.875
There's no strange illness
he hasn't seen.

00:12:09.625 --> 00:12:10.708
He won't take it to heart.

00:12:12.958 --> 00:12:13.750
This illness of mine

00:12:14.916 --> 00:12:16.500
may never be cured.

00:12:18.750 --> 00:12:19.625
This is an illness of the heart.

00:12:20.791 --> 00:12:21.666
Once the inner demon is gone,

00:12:22.375 --> 00:12:23.208
you will heal without medicine.

00:12:25.208 --> 00:12:26.000
Inner demon?

00:12:27.333 --> 00:12:27.916
Leng Xin?

00:12:29.875 --> 00:12:31.833
Deep down,

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:37.333
are you

00:12:37.833 --> 00:12:38.666
terrified of Leng Xin?

00:12:47.875 --> 00:12:48.541
Yes.

00:12:49.958 --> 00:12:50.833
I'm afraid of him.

00:12:52.958 --> 00:12:54.583
I'm afraid I will never defeat him.

00:12:55.500 --> 00:12:57.375
That I will never avenge my father.

00:12:58.750 --> 00:13:00.458
And I'm even more afraid

00:13:00.875 --> 00:13:01.958
he will hurt everyone
who has helped me.

00:13:02.791 --> 00:13:03.916
I don't want to drag anyone down.

00:13:06.041 --> 00:13:07.166
With so much fear,

00:13:07.750 --> 00:13:08.500
how can you take revenge?

00:13:11.166 --> 00:13:12.000
I know.

00:13:13.958 --> 00:13:15.083
But I'm still afraid.

00:13:16.875 --> 00:13:17.916
I faced Diaotu

00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:19.458
and Liu Sankong without fear.

00:13:21.250 --> 00:13:22.500
But I'm afraid of Leng Xin.

00:13:23.916 --> 00:13:25.375
I'm afraid I can't catch him.

00:13:26.625 --> 00:13:28.500
I'm afraid he will
keep hurting the people around me.

00:13:30.333 --> 00:13:30.875
Sometimes,

00:13:30.875 --> 00:13:32.375
I feel so cowardly and weak.

00:13:33.875 --> 00:13:34.625
I'm not even

00:13:36.750 --> 00:13:38.916
as carefree as Xintian.

00:13:40.458 --> 00:13:41.041
Bingfan.

00:13:42.625 --> 00:13:44.000
Because of Leng Xin,

00:13:47.083 --> 00:13:49.333
you were left with a wound
that won't fade.

00:13:50.541 --> 00:13:51.541
But you don't need to be afraid.

00:13:52.166 --> 00:13:53.416
You are not fighting alone.

00:13:54.375 --> 00:13:55.750
You have everyone, and you have me.

00:13:57.166 --> 00:13:58.166
No matter how powerful Leng Xin is,

00:13:58.916 --> 00:14:00.166
he is still flesh and blood.

00:14:01.125 --> 00:14:02.375
As long as we stand together,

00:14:02.375 --> 00:14:03.541
we can defeat him.

00:14:05.958 --> 00:14:06.500
Really?

00:14:11.208 --> 00:14:12.041
There is truly nothing to fear.

00:14:13.000 --> 00:14:13.875
As long as I'm here,

00:14:15.958 --> 00:14:17.708
I will never let Leng Xin hurt you.

00:14:24.310 --> 00:14:29.020
♪In a fleeting moment♪

00:14:30.720 --> 00:14:35.020
♪Whose face crosses my mind♪

00:14:37.270 --> 00:14:42.060
♪Whose name is it♪

00:14:43.180 --> 00:14:47.430
♪I whisper in my heart♪

00:14:47.430 --> 00:14:54.330
♪Yet in the crowd, we brush past♪

00:14:55.180 --> 00:14:58.350
♪Only then did I understand fate♪

00:14:58.350 --> 00:15:02.020
♪Was hidden in the day we met♪

00:15:02.890 --> 00:15:06.390
♪A fate that can't be severed♪

00:15:07.390 --> 00:15:09.720
♪Round and round♪

00:15:09.930 --> 00:15:14.180
♪Threads of love bind us together♪

00:15:14.180 --> 00:15:18.810
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

00:15:20.430 --> 00:15:26.640
♪Afraid memories will vanish
like dreams♪

00:15:26.770 --> 00:15:30.390
♪This longing I can't say♪

00:15:30.600 --> 00:15:35.560
♪I wish you could hear♪

00:15:46.833 --> 00:15:47.250
Xintian.

00:15:48.875 --> 00:15:50.041
Bingfan.

00:15:50.583 --> 00:15:51.666
I was sleeping just fine.

00:15:51.666 --> 00:15:53.000
Why did you kick me?

00:15:56.791 --> 00:15:58.208
When did I fall asleep last night?

00:15:58.541 --> 00:15:59.916
You fell asleep very early.

00:16:00.291 --> 00:16:01.416
When I came back from night duty,

00:16:01.625 --> 00:16:02.708
you were already asleep.

00:16:04.500 --> 00:16:05.791
Was it another dream?

00:16:06.166 --> 00:16:06.666
A dream?

00:16:07.583 --> 00:16:09.000
What did you dream about, Bingfan?

00:16:10.833 --> 00:16:11.458
Nothing.

00:16:13.166 --> 00:16:14.333
Why are you on the floor?

00:16:14.500 --> 00:16:15.875
You kicked me down here.

00:16:23.875 --> 00:16:24.875
Go back to sleep.

00:16:51.583 --> 00:16:52.000
Bingfan.

00:16:52.541 --> 00:16:53.250
Guan.

00:16:55.750 --> 00:16:56.875
What is all this?

00:16:57.083 --> 00:16:58.250
I heard you have been
having trouble sleeping.

00:16:58.500 --> 00:16:59.291
So I found

00:17:00.000 --> 00:17:01.166
a folk remedy for insomnia.

00:17:02.083 --> 00:17:02.833
What remedy?

00:17:04.708 --> 00:17:05.208
Wine?

00:17:06.833 --> 00:17:07.208
Yes.

00:17:07.500 --> 00:17:09.500
Wine is the best cure for insomnia.

00:17:09.791 --> 00:17:11.125
It has been passed down for ages

00:17:11.250 --> 00:17:12.000
and never fails.

00:17:12.416 --> 00:17:13.250
A few cups,

00:17:13.458 --> 00:17:15.416
and you will sleep straight through
till morning.

00:17:15.541 --> 00:17:16.541
It's cheap and effective,

00:17:16.666 --> 00:17:17.583
and you can buy it anywhere.

00:17:18.541 --> 00:17:20.791
But I never drink.

00:17:21.916 --> 00:17:22.958
That's why it works.

00:17:23.375 --> 00:17:25.000
If you could hold your liquor,

00:17:25.500 --> 00:17:26.416
it wouldn't work.

00:17:28.083 --> 00:17:29.125
But I can't

00:17:29.791 --> 00:17:32.125
drink every night before bed.

00:17:32.208 --> 00:17:33.208
You can try it first.

00:17:33.250 --> 00:17:33.958
What if it works?

00:17:34.708 --> 00:17:36.458
What if she's addicted to it?

00:17:38.083 --> 00:17:39.458
Hua, why would you say that?

00:17:40.666 --> 00:17:43.208
Constable Guan, you enjoy wine.

00:17:44.250 --> 00:17:45.500
So you should know

00:17:45.708 --> 00:17:48.666
that the more one drinks,
the more one can drink.

00:17:49.458 --> 00:17:52.583
If Bingfan uses wine as medicine
every night,

00:17:52.791 --> 00:17:54.375
in less than three months,

00:17:54.708 --> 00:17:57.083
she will be drinking everyone
under the table.

00:17:57.666 --> 00:17:59.791
Are you trying to turn Bingfan

00:17:59.916 --> 00:18:01.791
into an alcoholic?

00:18:04.500 --> 00:18:05.583
No, no.

00:18:05.583 --> 00:18:06.791
That's not what I meant.

00:18:07.458 --> 00:18:09.125
Bingfan, I really didn't mean that.

00:18:11.375 --> 00:18:12.833
I'll find another remedy.

00:18:22.625 --> 00:18:24.041
He's cute.

00:18:43.600 --> 00:18:46.770
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:47.140 --> 00:18:50.520
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:50.770 --> 00:18:53.770
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:53.770 --> 00:18:57.180
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:18:58.270 --> 00:19:01.480
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:19:01.890 --> 00:19:05.230
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:05.810 --> 00:19:08.020
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:08.020 --> 00:19:12.060
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:12.060 --> 00:19:15.930
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:15.930 --> 00:19:19.680
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:19.980 --> 00:19:21.890
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:21.890 --> 00:19:26.430
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:26.730 --> 00:19:28.230
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:28.230 --> 00:19:30.600
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:30.600 --> 00:19:34.480
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:34.480 --> 00:19:36.810
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:36.810 --> 00:19:41.810
♪And run toward this vast life♪